Neimeth Nigeria to Raise 1.23 Billion Naira in Rights Offer

-- B y   V i n c e n t   N w a n m a
-- 
2011-09-23T11:39:59Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-09-23/neimeth-nigeria-to-raise-1-23-billion-naira-in-rights-offer.html
Neimeth International
Pharmaceuticals Plc (NEIMETH)  of  Nigeria  plans to raise 1.23 billion naira
by offering 821.6 million shares, Michael Ogun, head of
corporate finance at Lagos-based Meristem Securities Ltd., the
issuer, said today in a phone interview.  The shares will be sold at 1.50 naira each starting Sept.
27 if the Securities and Exchange Commission gives approval
before then, he said.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Vincent Nwanma in Lagos at 
 vnwanma@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Dulue Mbachu at 
 dmbachu@bloomberg.net  